methods.isResolvable:
Returns true if the resolver can resolve the uri.

:param uri: (java.net.URI) - the uri
:return: (boolean) true if this resolver can resolve uri
methods.resolve:
Resolve uri into an object.

*Overload 1*  
  :param uri: (java.net.URI) - the URI
  :return: (java.lang.Object) the object
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param uri: io.deephaven.uri.QueryScopeUri
  :return: java.lang.Object
  
*Overload 3*  
  :param variableName: java.lang.String
  :return: java.lang.Object

The query scope table resolver is able to resolve query scope URIs.

 
 For example, dh:///scope/my_table.
